Eloquent ORM adalah implementasi Active Record pattern di Laravel untuk berinteraksi dengan database. Setiap tabel database memiliki Model yang corresponding. Contoh:

class User extends Model {
    protected $table = 'users';
    protected $fillable = ['name', 'email', 'password'];
}

Untuk query: User::all(), User::find(1), User::where('email', $email)->first()

Untuk membuat controller di Laravel:
1. Gunakan artisan command: php artisan make:controller NamaController
2. Untuk resource controller: php artisan make:controller NamaController --resource
3. Controller akan dibuat di app/Http/Controllers/
4. Contoh isi controller:

namespace App\Http\Controllers;

use Illuminate\Http\Request;

class UserController extends Controller {
    public function index() {
        return view('users.index');
    }
}

Untuk membuat migration:
1. Command: php artisan make:migration create_users_table
2. File migration ada di database/migrations/
3. Edit method up() untuk create table dan down() untuk drop table
4. Contoh:

public function up() {
    Schema::create('users', function (Blueprint $table) {
        $table->id();
        $table->string('name');
        $table->string('email')->unique();
        $table->timestamps();
    });
}

5. Jalankan migration: php artisan migrate

Routes di Laravel didefinisikan di folder routes/. Untuk web routes, gunakan routes/web.php:

// Basic route
Route::get('/home', function () {
    return view('home');
});

// Route ke controller
Route::get('/users', [UserController::class, 'index']);

// Route dengan parameter
Route::get('/user/{id}', [UserController::class, 'show']);

// Resource route (CRUD otomatis)
Route::resource('posts', PostController::class);

Middleware adalah filter untuk HTTP request. Berguna untuk authentication, logging, CORS, dll.

Cara membuat:
1. Command: php artisan make:middleware CheckAge
2. Edit file di app/Http/Middleware/CheckAge.php:

public function handle($request, Closure $next) {
    if ($request->age <= 18) {
        return redirect('home');
    }
    return $next($request);
}

3. Daftarkan di app/Http/Kernel.php
4. Gunakan di route: Route::get('/admin', function () {...})->middleware('checkage');

Seeder digunakan untuk mengisi database dengan data dummy:

1. Buat seeder: php artisan make:seeder UserSeeder
2. Edit database/seeders/UserSeeder.php:

public function run() {
    User::create([
        'name' => 'Admin',
        'email' => 'admin@example.com',
        'password' => Hash::make('password')
    ]);
}

3. Panggil di DatabaseSeeder.php:
public function run() {
    $this->call(UserSeeder::class);
}

4. Jalankan: php artisan db:seed

Factory digunakan untuk generate data testing:

1. Buat factory: php artisan make:factory PostFactory
2. Edit database/factories/PostFactory.php:

public function definition() {
    return [
        'title' => $this->faker->sentence(),
        'content' => $this->faker->paragraph(),
        'user_id' => User::factory(),
    ];
}

3. Gunakan di seeder atau test:
Post::factory()->count(50)->create();

4. Dengan relationship:
User::factory()
    ->has(Post::factory()->count(3))
    ->create();

Laravel menyediakan validation yang powerful:

1. Di controller:
public function store(Request $request) {
    $validated = $request->validate([
        'title' => 'required|max:255',
        'email' => 'required|email|unique:users',
        'password' => 'required|min:8|confirmed',
        'age' => 'required|numeric|min:18',
    ]);
    // Process validated data
}

2. Atau buat Form Request:
php artisan make:request StorePostRequest

Edit rules():
public function rules() {
    return [
        'title' => 'required|max:255',
        'content' => 'required',
    ];
}

Eloquent mendukung berbagai relationship:

1. One to One:
class User extends Model {
    public function profile() {
        return $this->hasOne(Profile::class);
    }
}

2. One to Many:
class Post extends Model {
    public function comments() {
        return $this->hasMany(Comment::class);
    }
}

3. Many to Many:
class User extends Model {
    public function roles() {
        return $this->belongsToMany(Role::class);
    }
}

4. Akses relationship:
$user->profile
$post->comments
$user->roles

Laravel menyediakan caching API yang unified:

1. Setup cache driver di .env (file, redis, memcached, dll)

2. Basic usage:
// Store cache
Cache::put('key', 'value', $seconds);
Cache::forever('key', 'value');

// Retrieve cache
$value = Cache::get('key');
$value = Cache::get('key', 'default');

// Remember (get or store)
$value = Cache::remember('users', 3600, function () {
    return DB::table('users')->get();
});

3. Clear cache:
Cache::forget('key');
Cache::flush();
php artisan cache:clear

Untuk membuat RESTful API di Laravel:

1. Gunakan routes/api.php untuk API routes
2. Buat API controller:
php artisan make:controller API/UserController --api

3. Contoh controller:
public function index() {
    return response()->json(User::all());
}

public function store(Request $request) {
    $user = User::create($request->validated());
    return response()->json($user, 201);
}

4. API Resources untuk format response:
php artisan make:resource UserResource

5. Authentication dengan Sanctum:
composer require laravel/sanctum
php artisan sanctum:install
